quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Ԑberε a Abͻfoͻ no baa Lut nkorͻfoͻ no hͻ no
  15,62,"Ɔkaa sε: ”Nokorε sε moyε nnipa bi a menni mo, (anaasε moyε ahͻhoͻ”)"
  15,63,"Abͻfoͻ no kaa sε: ”Daabi, yεde (asotwee) a wͻn adwen nnsi wͻn pi wͻ ho no na yεde aba wo hͻ"
  15,64,"Nokorε na yεde abrε woͻ no, na ampa sε nokorε na yεreka no"
  15,65,"Enti fa w’abusuafoͻ no tu kwan anadwo, na di wͻn akyi, na hwε na momu biara antwa n’ani anhwε n’akyi, na mmom monkͻ faako a yahyε mo (sε monkͻ) no"
  15,66,"Yε’maa no hunuu saa nhyehyεε no sε, saa nkorͻfoͻ no akyiri akwan bεyera anͻpa tutuutu"
  15,67,Kuro no mu foͻ no de anigyeε bae
  15,68,"Lut kaa sε: ”Nokorε sε woi nom yε m’ahͻhoͻ enti monhwε na moangu m’anim ase (wͻ wͻn anim)"
  15,69,"Na monsuro Nyankopͻn, na monngu m’anim ase.“"
  15,70,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Yε’mraa wo sε gyae nnipa (ahͻho gyeε?”)"
  15,71,"Lut kaa sε: ”Sε mobεyε saa deε a εneε memma mmaa nie “"
  15,72,"(Nkͻmhyεni), Mede wonkwa di nse sε, nokorε, na wͻn wͻ anifira nsaborͻ mu redi akͻneaba"
  15,73,Enti nteamu denden no sͻͻ wͻn mu awia pue berε
  15,74,"Na Yε’danee (Sodom kuro) no ani butuu no, na Yε’tͻͻ aboͻ nsuo a efri Sijiil mu guu wͻn so"
  15,75,"Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu ma wͻn a wͻ’hunu adeε (anaa wͻ’dwen, anaa wͻ’de betu wͻn ho foͻ)"
  15,76,"Nokorε sε, (na saa nkuro no) wͻ, (efri Maka rekͻ Siria) ͻkwan tempͻn a εdaso wͻhͻ no so"
  15,77,Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu dema agyidiefoͻ no
  15,78,Na ‘Ayikat’ anaasε nkorͻfoͻ a na wͻ’te Nnua mu no nso yε abͻneεfoͻ
  15,79,Enti Ye’tuaa wͻn dwumadi bͻne no so ka. Wͻn mmienu no nyinaa wͻ ͻkwan tempͻn pefee no so